---
// ============================================================
// modules/sr/index.astro
// URL: /modules/sr
// Module overzichtspagina voor Special Relativity
//
// Kopieer dit bestand voor elke nieuwe module en pas aan:
//   - modColor → de juiste --mod-xxx variabele
//   - activeNav → de module-ID
//   - icon, titel, beschrijving
//   - De lessenlijst onderaan
// ============================================================
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Special Relativity · Quantum Leap Physics</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/global.css" />
  <style>
    /* ── Modulekleur voor deze pagina ── */
    :root { --mod-color: var(--mod-sr); }

    /* ── Module index layout ── */
    .main-module-index {
      margin-left: var(--sidebar-w);
      margin-top: var(--header-h);
      max-width: 860px;
      padding: 48px;
    }

    /* ── Module hero ── */
    .module-index-hero {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .module-index-hero__top {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .module-index-hero__icon {
      font-size: 52px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px color-mix(in srgb, var(--mod-color) 50%, transparent));
    }
    .module-index-hero__meta {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--mod-color); letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .module-index-hero__title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .module-index-hero__desc { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; }
    .module-index-hero__stats {
      display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-top: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .hero-stat { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

    /* ── Lessenlijst ── */
    .lessons-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .lessons-list__header {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .lesson-row {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
      text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
      transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .lesson-row::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 3px;
      background: var(--mod-color); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    .lesson-row:hover { background: var(--bg-card-hover); border-color: var(--border-light); transform: translateX(2px); }
    .lesson-row:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .lesson-row.locked { opacity: 0.45; cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }

    .lesson-row__status {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px;
    }
    .lesson-row__status--done   { background: var(--mod-color); color: #0d0f1a; font-weight: 700; }
    .lesson-row__status--active { background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--mod-color); color: var(--mod-color); }
    .lesson-row__status--todo   { background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--border-light); color: var(--text-muted); }

    .lesson-row__body { flex: 1; }
    .lesson-row__code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .lesson-row__title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
    .lesson-row__desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 3px; }

    .lesson-row__meta {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);
      text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .lesson-row__cta {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--mod-color); flex-shrink: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar__logo">
    <div class="sidebar__logo-wordmark">Quantum<span>Leap</span></div>
    <div class="sidebar__logo-sub">Physics Platform</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <div class="sidebar__section-label">Learn</div>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/dashboard"><span class="nav-item__icon">🏠</span> Dashboard</a>
    <a class="nav-item active" href="/modules/sr"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-sr)">⚡</span> Special Relativity</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/modules/qm"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-qm)">🌀</span> Quantum Mechanics</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/modules/em"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-em)">🔵</span> Electrodynamics</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/modules/ana"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-ana)">📐</span> Analytical Mechanics</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/modules/sm"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-sm)">🌡️</span> Statistical Mechanics</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/modules/qft"><span class="nav-item__icon" style="color:var(--mod-qft)">✴️</span> Quantum Field Theory</a>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <div class="sidebar__section-label">My Progress</div>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#"><span class="nav-item__icon">📊</span> Activity</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#"><span class="nav-item__icon">🗺️</span> Knowledge Map</a>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <div class="sidebar__section-label">Account</div>
    <a class="nav-item" href="/"><span class="nav-item__icon">🌐</span> Homepage</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#"><span class="nav-item__icon">⚙️</span> Settings</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="https://patreon.com/quantumleapphysics" target="_blank"><span class="nav-item__icon">❤️</span> Patreon</a>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar__user">
    <div class="sidebar__avatar">M</div>
    <div>
      <div class="sidebar__user-name">Mathis</div>
      <div class="sidebar__user-role">Supporter</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="header__breadcrumb">
    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
    <span class="sep">›</span>
    <span class="current">Special Relativity</span>
  </div>
  <div class="header__right">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-outline">← Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/modules/sr/sr-01" class="btn-primary">Start module →</a>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="main-module-index">

  <!-- Module hero -->
  <div class="module-index-hero">
    <div class="module-index-hero__top">
      <div class="module-index-hero__icon">⚡</div>
      <div>
        <div class="module-index-hero__meta">SR · Module 1</div>
        <h1 class="module-index-hero__title">Special Relativity</h1>
        <p class="module-index-hero__desc">
          Time dilation, length contraction, E=mc². Why Newton breaks down at high speeds —
          and what replaces him. We start with thought experiments, not formulas.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="module-index-hero__stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><span>📄</span> 8 lessons</div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><span>🕐</span> ~9 hours total</div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><span>✅</span> 3 of 8 done</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Lessons list -->
  <div class="lessons-list__header">All lessons</div>
  <div class="lessons-list">

    <!-- ============================================================
         LESSENLIJST
         Pas aan voor elke module:
           - href: /modules/sr/sr-XX
           - status class: --done / --active / --todo
           - statusinhoud: ✓ / ● / lesnummer
           - code, titel, beschrijving, duur
         ============================================================ -->

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-01">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--done">✓</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-01</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">Why Newton Falls Short</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">The Michelson-Morley experiment and the crisis of classical physics.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">45 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-02">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--done">✓</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-02</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">The Speed of Light</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">Einstein's two postulates and what they imply.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">60 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-03">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--active">●</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-03</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">Time Dilation</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">Moving clocks run slow. The light clock thought experiment.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">75 min</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__cta">Continue →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-04">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--todo">4</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-04</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">Length Contraction</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">Moving objects are shorter. The barn-pole paradox.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">60 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-05">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--todo">5</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-05</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">Simultaneity</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">Two events simultaneous in one frame need not be in another.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">50 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-06">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--todo">6</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-06</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">The Spacetime Interval</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">The quantity all observers agree on. Minkowski spacetime.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">70 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-07">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--todo">7</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-07</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">Relativistic Energy & Momentum</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">Why mass and energy are the same thing.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">80 min</div>
    </a>

    <a class="lesson-row" href="/modules/sr/sr-08">
      <div class="lesson-row__status lesson-row__status--todo">8</div>
      <div class="lesson-row__body">
        <div class="lesson-row__code">SR-08</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__title">E = mc²</div>
        <div class="lesson-row__desc">The most famous equation in physics — where it actually comes from.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-row__meta">65 min</div>
    </a>

  </div>

</main>

</body>
</html>
